ZH: 他每天早晨都在花园里给花浇水。
EN: He waters the flowers in the garden every morning.

ZH: 妈妈让我去浇菜地里的蔬菜。
EN: Mom asked me to water the vegetables in the vegetable garden.

ZH: 我费了整整一个小时才把花盆浇透。
EN: It took me a whole hour to thoroughly water the flowerpot.

ZH: 外公每天都喜欢在院子里浇水。
EN: Grandpa enjoys watering the yard every day.

ZH: 这盆植物需要定期浇水。
EN: This plant needs to be watered regularly.

ZH: 小孩子们在公园里欢快地浇水。
EN: The children happily watered the plants in the park.

ZH: 看到蔬菜枯萎了，我赶紧给它们浇了水。
EN: Seeing the vegetables withered, I quickly watered them.

ZH: 我们需要浇透这片土地才能开始种植。
EN: We need to water this piece of land thoroughly before planting.

ZH: 请记得每天都要浇水给植物。
EN: Please remember to water the plants every day.

ZH: 外婆说要浇少许过的盐水给香菜。
EN: Grandma said to water the coriander with a little salt water.

ZH: 在夏天，植物需要的水量比较大，要多浇水。
EN: In summer, plants require more water and need to be watered more.

ZH: 玫瑰花需要浇水和喷洒养分。
EN: Rose flowers need to be watered and sprayed with nutrients.

ZH: 她花了很多的时间在院子里浇水。
EN: She spent a lot of time watering the yard.

ZH: 浇水的时候，要把水均匀地洒在土壤上。
EN: When watering, make sure to evenly sprinkle water on the soil.

ZH: 开始浇水之前，我们要先检查植物的湿度。
EN: Before starting to water, we need to check the moisture level of the plants.

ZH: 看到植物正在枯萎，他决定要马上浇水。
EN: Seeing the plants wilting, he decided to water them immediately.

ZH: 请确保不要过度浇水，以免植物受损。
EN: Please make sure not to overwater to prevent damage to the plants.

ZH: 每次浇水的时候，都要看看植物的叶子是否有生病。
EN: Every time you water, check to see if the plant's leaves are diseased.

ZH: 浇水的同时也要施肥以促进植物的生长。
EN: Fertilize while watering to promote plant growth.
